\vert x-c\vert^2=\vert x-y\vert^2+\vert y-c\vert^2+2\langle x-y\mid y-c\rangle
\begin{array}{ccl}\langle x-y\mid y-c\rangle &=&\langle y-p\mid y-c\rangle\\ &=&\langle y-p\mid y-p\rangle+\langle y-p\mid p-c\rangle\\ &=&\vert y-p\vert^2-\langle y-p\mid c-p\rangle\\ &\geq&\vert y-p\vert^2\\ &>&0 \end{array}
